title: Brand New amateur youtube channel :)

embed.title: KetorinoEditing
embed.description: Photo and video editing, passionate of gameplay mashups. Looking for collaborations! email: ketorino.editing@gmail.com

body:
Hey guys! I just started this new channel as I'm coming back to league.
Would be cool if you check it out and support it (subscribe, comment on the videos i'll upload in the next days), motivating me to editing more :)

Thanks to everyone who will give it a check :) i'm into a new series of video now "all champs plays", while i work on a cool idea i have in mind :)
Also if you want to be part of it, send me your plays at ketorino.editing@gmail.com
Have a nice game guys, bye!
